## Quick Reference for Inline Styles

When you must use inline styles (e.g., dynamic values), always include the font:

```tsx
// For body text sizes (15px, 14px, 13px, 12px)
style={{ fontFamily: 'var(--font-sans)', fontSize: 15 }}

// For display/title sizes (34px, 28px, 19px+)
style={{ fontFamily: 'var(--font-display)', fontSize: 28 }}
```
